 A new event display for the KLOE-2 experiment: 
 http://arxiv.org/abs/1501.04454: 
 10.5506/APhysPolB.46.95: 
 None: 
 17: 
   In this contribution we describe KNEDLE - the new event display for the
KLOE-2 experiment. The basic objectives and software requirements are
presented. The current status of the development is given along with a short
discussion of the future plans.
