 Studies of mesic nuclei via decay reactions: 
 http://arxiv.org/abs/1401.0747: 
 10.5506/APhysPolB.45.745: 
 Acta Phys. Polon. B 45, 745 (2014): 
 15: 
   Collisions in a system of two particles at energies close to a bound state in
different channels are discussed. Next, the bound state decays into a third
coupled channel. A phenomenological approach to dd->pi-p3He reaction is
presented.
